instagram.content: Doing religion right at the church of Darcelle XV, 87 years outrageous. You walk in looking for a naughty giggle and walk out inspired to show the world who you really are, lumps and all. Thank you lovely ladies! Some of the men in the group shot—no  exaggeration—saved my life as we got together each week to share our pain and struggles.  Alchemists of the highest order, we turned our shit into platinum, and I wouldn’t be where I am without them. Much gratitude. Happy 60th, Dan! #SomeHeroesRockFalseEyelashesAndAWig

8.content: It's an occupational hazard: the spark that inspires entrepreneurs to go into business can be squelched by the day-to-day challenges of managing its growth. Sage's digital accounting products make it easy to stay on top of your finances, allowing business owners to get back to doing what they love. We comped up a few stories that said "goodbye" to these business headaches and "hello" to a smoother, more fulfilling operation.
